1946;;The Scarlet Horseman;;American;;Lewis D. Collins, Ray Taylor;;Peter Cookson, Paul Guilfoyle;;serial;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Scarlet_Horseman;;Two Texas Rangers investigate the kidnapping of wives and daughters of Senators. In order to do so, one goes undercover as "The Scarlet Horseman", a legendary and respected Comanche figure. The villainess, Matosca, intends to use the kidnappees to force a partition of Texas.